{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.120", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.040", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um Afghanistan die Perspektive auf eine friedliche Zukunft zu er\u00f6ffnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.600", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind Schritte zur Verhinderung erneuter Anarchie im \u00f6ffentlichen Leben vordringlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "...\u00a0Daher sollten Sicherheit und Ordnung mit Unterst\u00fctzung der internationalen Gemeinschaft gew\u00e4hrleistet\u00a0\u2026 werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit diesen Worten beantragte die Bundesregierung im Dezember\u00a02001 das erste Mandat zur Entsendung deutscher Soldaten nach Afghanistan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.160", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Inzwischen dauert der Krieg dort bald 17\u00a0Jahre an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.720", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was als gutgemeinter Versuch begann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um mit den Worten des Vorsitzenden des Deutschen BundeswehrVerbandes zu sprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als \u201eMachbarkeitsillusion\u201c entpuppt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem vorliegenden Antrag der Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.320", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Einsatz deutscher Soldaten in Afghanistan erneut zu verl\u00e4ngern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.720", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird an diese Machbarkeitsillusion angekn\u00fcpft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anstatt endlich eine ehrliche Bilanz zu ziehen und das offensichtliche Scheitern des Westens am Hindukusch einzugestehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bef\u00fcrworter des Mandats\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hat die Ministerin gerade wieder angesprochen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden nicht m\u00fcde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu betonen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.320", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es in Afghanistan auch punktuelle Erfolge gegeben hat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wird gar nicht bestritten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.640", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es dort inzwischen Medien gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.600", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es Wahlen gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.680", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass mehr Menschen Zugang zu Trinkwasser und Strom haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch nicht gesagt worden ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wird noch kommen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass mehr afghanische Kinder die Schule besuchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.680", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das mag alles stimmen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber das war gar nicht die Aufgabe der NATO und auch nicht die Aufgabe der Bundeswehr in Afghanistan."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Aufgaben waren die Herstellung von \u00f6ffentlicher Sicherheit und Ordnung und die Reform des Sicherheitssektors."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Machbarkeitsillusion ist an der Wirklichkeit gescheitert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Gesamtbilanz ist verheerend:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz der seit 2001 andauernden Versuche der internationalen Gemeinschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechtsstaatlichkeit und demokratische Strukturen zu etablieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "geh\u00f6rt Afghanistan zu den korruptesten L\u00e4ndern der Welt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz der Bem\u00fchungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Opiumanbau zu unterbinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.320", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der den Aufst\u00e4ndischen als wesentliche Einnahmequelle dient, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist Afghanistan zum weltweit gr\u00f6\u00dften Produzenten von Opium aufgestiegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz der umfangreichen und \u00fcber 15\u00a0Jahre andauernden Ausbildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beratung und Unterst\u00fctzung der afghanischen Sicherheitskr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "trotz modernster Milit\u00e4rtechnologie aus dem Westen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drohnenangriffen und Gro\u00dfoffensiven gibt es weder Besiegte noch Sieger in diesem Krieg. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.280", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weite Teile des Landes sind eben nicht unter der Kontrolle der Regierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Anzahl ziviler Opfer ist h\u00f6her denn je, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.640", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und noch immer fliehen Hundertausende Afghanen innerhalb der Landesgrenzen und auch nach Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.200", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Jahr\u00a02000 stellten rund 5\u00a0400\u00a0Afghanen einen Asylantrag in Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.720", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im vergangenen Jahr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.680", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "waren es 227\u00a0000\u00a0Asylantr\u00e4ge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind 42\u2011mal mehr als auf dem H\u00f6hepunkt der Herrschaft der Taliban."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und jetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verehrte Bundesregierung und Frau Verteidigungsministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wollen Sie erneut deutsche Soldaten zur Staatenrettung nach Afghanistan schicken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend afghanische Fl\u00fcchtlinge auf dem Ku\u2019damm Kaffee trinken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.760", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anstatt beim Wiederaufbau ihres Landes zu helfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Korruption, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drogen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Terroranschl\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Chaos und Flucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.840", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist die Bilanz in Afghanistan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im vorliegenden Antrag der Bundesregierung zur Verl\u00e4ngerung der Resolute Support Mission in Afghanistan hei\u00dft es: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aufgabe der Mission ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.400", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201edie afghanischen nationalen ... "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.960", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherheitskr\u00e4fte zu bef\u00e4higen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihrer Sicherheitsverantwortung nachzukommen\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.640", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist und bleibt eine Machbarkeitsillusion. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mehr noch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.200", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist politischer Unsinn. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.200", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist der gleiche Unsinn wie die Aussage \u201eDeutschlands Sicherheit wird am Hindukusch verteidigt\u201c."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.520", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.120", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.560", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschlands Sicherheit wird nicht am Hindukusch verteidigt,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "307.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern an der deutschen und europ\u00e4ischen Au\u00dfengrenze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "307.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "326.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD-Fraktion lehnt den Antrag der Bundesregierung deshalb ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "326.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.360", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Gauland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "328.360", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe vergessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "328.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "329.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darauf hinzuweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "329.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dies Ihre erste Rede im Deutschen Bundestag ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "338.840", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hole ich hiermit nach."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "338.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "343.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als n\u00e4chster Redner hat nunmehr Alexander Graf Lambsdorff das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}